      <title>德勤：到 2030 年，超级富裕家庭将控制 9.5 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ultra-rich-families-set-to-control-9-5-trillion-by-2030-deloitte-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据咨询公司德勤估计，随着家族理财室的壮大并转变为与对冲基金竞争，到 2030 年，超级富豪家族的财富可能将膨胀至 9.5 万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ultra-rich-families-set-to-control-9-5-trillion-by-2030-deloitte-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 13:01:48 GMT</pubDate>
